snippet.title: Freddy Fazbear Pizzeria Simulator VR (W.I.P)
snippet.description:
This is another VR game that I am working on and will be releasing soon. This is just a video showing an early but stable version of the game.

All rights go to Scott Cawthon, creator of the Five Night's at Freddy's franchise. This game will be free and no money will be made from it.

Link to the game page: https://gamejolt.com/games/FFPSVR/423554
